  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with cirrhosis have a altered cardiac response to stress. This study evaluate the
      cardiac response by MRI during dobutamine stress. Hypothesis: impared increase in cardiac
      output, cardiac index, ejection fraction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
